# Local / device debug defaults. No bearer token/secret belongs in this file
# — the client session token is minted at runtime (POST /v1/session) and
# stored only in Keychain. See docs/SECURITY.md.
#
# Xcode treats `//` as a comment, so we split the scheme with `/$()/`.
#
# Dewey public tunnel (Cloudflare → bridge :8787). Use this so a physical
# device or a Simulator that can't reach Dewey's LAN still hits the bridge.
# For a bridge running only on your Mac, switch back to:
#   BRIDGE_BASE_URL = http:/$()/localhost:8787
BRIDGE_BASE_URL = https:/$()/dewey-bridge.momentumclaw.app
